name: Releases Drafter
description:
Automate Drafts your next release notes as PullRequests are merged into main brach. Version Release be resolved automatically based on labels of individual pull requests.
Append the following file 'https://github.com/pagonxt/.github/blob/master/.github/release-drafter.yml' into your '.github' folder. Official Project and Docs: https://github.com/release-drafter/release-drafter
